You can also create different page variations and assign a particular page to a different set of target
audiences
In the expereince cloud design builder > Home > Page variations > duplicate > create new one and name it 
> configure the page accordingly > and add assign > assign it to different set of users
Users are be filtered through their user record fields, or roles or profiles

You can also assign particular components to target audience also. Click the drop down arrow
on the components and assign your target audiences

Brading sets: customize different colos, fonts and images for different target audiences
Go to themes component > manage branding sets > create a new one and assign your target audiences

components in header and footer sections can't be targeted to specific target audiences
